README
======

System requirements
-------------------

Compiling this code requires the following:
 * cmake version 2.6 or later
 * boost C++ libraries
 * GNU Bison (version 2.4.2 should do, earlier version may also work)
 * Flex (version 2.5.35 should do, earlier version may also work)
 * Compilers for C and C++ code
   * GCC and clang are known to work


Compile instructions
--------------------

In the root project directory do the following:

  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake ..
  make

Executable will be placed in build/bin directory and libraries in build/lib.
